data.description: This beautiful 2 story home in highly sought Rancho El Dorado, will make you say, ''this is the one!'' Beautiful wood tile all down-stairs, formal living/dining room, walk to the back to the family room.  Nice space that opens to the kitchen. Kitchen has granite counter-tops, tiled backsplash, matching appliances, all neutral colors. Upstairs, main bedroom descent sized w/ ample closet space. All other bedrooms are good sized. The backyard has a nice covered patio, for nice gatherings. Green grassy area , backyard is just perfect size. Upgrades, newer A/C 2016, exterior paint 2018, flooring-granite all around 2019-2020. Come see this one!
